<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3778659>
    dc:description "Figs 14-17. Cormocephalus gervaisianus: 14 – head plate; 15 – forcipular coxosternum and forcipules; 16 – terminal tergite and prefemur of ultimate leg, dorsal view; 17 – prefemur of ultimate leg, ventral view." ;
